defaultAccessdefault to finance, particularly for Small and Medium Enterprisesdefault default&#xa0;
defaultThe Government recognises that access to finance remains a significant challenge for SMEs in 
defaultNorthern Ireland
default, as it does across the 
defaultUK
default. The Northern Ireland Department for 
defaultEnterprise
default, Trade and Investment’s Economic Advisory Group (EAG) produced a detailed report on access to finance in 
defaultNorthern Ireland
default.
default&#xa0;
defaultThe report included the following conclusions:
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
defaultThe measures set out in our 
defaultBuilding a Prosperous and United Community
default package provide a comprehensive framework within which the Government intends to co-ordinate its efforts to boost lending to businesses in 
defaultNorthern Ireland
default. 
